---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - That's interesting.">
  <Header currentPage="about" />

  <main class="about-container">
    <div class="about-content">
      <h1 class="about-title">About</h1>

      <div class="about-intro">
        <p class="intro-text">
          Every day, we stumble upon facts that make us pause, lean forward, and think:
          <em>"That's interesting."</em> This site is a collection of those moments.
        </p>
      </div>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">The Mission</h2>
        <p>
          Knowledge shouldn't feel like homework. It should spark curiosity, connect unexpected dots,
          and rewire how we see the world. From quantum mechanics to medieval art, from cosmic
          collisions to linguistic quirks‚Äîif it shifts your perspective, it belongs here.
        </p>
        <p>
          We curate facts that hit that sweet spot between surprising and substantive. No clickbait,
          no fluff. Just well-researched discoveries that earn your attention.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">AI-Generated, Human-Curated</h2>
        <p>
          Let's be transparent: <strong>every fact on this site is generated by AI.</strong>
          Specifically, we use <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers-ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-link">Cloudflare Workers AI</a>
          running the <strong>GPT-OSS-120B</strong> model‚Äîa 120-billion parameter open-source language model.
        </p>
        <p>
          Why AI? Because in 2025, large language models have access to more knowledge than any
          individual human ever could. They can synthesize patterns across millions of papers, books,
          and data sources in seconds. They're not perfect, but they're often smarter than us at
          connecting disparate ideas and surfacing obscure facts.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>We can‚Äîand should‚Äîlearn from AI.</strong> Not blindly, but thoughtfully. Each
          generated fact includes sources, context, and a "wonder score" that helps you judge its
          significance. The goal isn't to replace human curiosity, but to amplify it.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">How It Works</h2>
        <div class="feature-list">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">‚ö°</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Generation</h3>
              <p>GPT-OSS-120B generates facts across 85+ domains, from astrophysics to linguistics.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">‚öñÔ∏è</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Scoring</h3>
              <p>Each fact gets a "wonder score" (1-10) measuring its surprise, depth, and verifiability.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">üîó</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Sources</h3>
              <p>Citations and related Wikipedia links help you explore deeper and verify claims.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">‚ú®</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Presentation</h3>
              <p>Beautiful, distraction-free design built with Astro and hosted on Cloudflare.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">The Tech Stack</h2>
        <ul class="tech-list">
          <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> Astro (static site generation)</li>
          <li><strong>AI Model:</strong> GPT-OSS-120B (120B parameters)</li>
          <li><strong>AI Platform:</strong> Cloudflare Workers AI</li>
          <li><strong>Hosting:</strong> Cloudflare Pages</li>
          <li><strong>Typography:</strong> Newsreader & Work Sans</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section disclaimer">
        <h2 class="section-title">A Note on Accuracy</h2>
        <p>
          AI-generated content can hallucinate facts or misattribute sources. While we've designed
          prompts to maximize accuracy and include citations, <strong>treat each fact as a starting
          point for exploration</strong>, not gospel truth. Always verify claims that matter to you.
        </p>
        <p>
          That said: in our testing, GPT-OSS-120B delivers highly accurate, well-sourced facts
          90%+ of the time. When it's right, it's spectacularly right. When it's wrong, it's usually
          obviously wrong. Use your judgment.
        </p>
      </section>

      <footer class="about-footer">
        <p>
          Built with curiosity. Powered by AI. <br>
          Questions? Find an error? We'd love to hear from you.
        </p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 750px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem var(--page-gutter) 6rem;
  }

  .about-content {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--black);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144;
  }

  .about-intro {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--black);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .intro-text em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grey-lighter);
  }

  .about-section:last-of-type {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--black);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 48;
  }

  .about-section p {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .inline-link {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }

  .inline-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* Feature List */
  .feature-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .feature-content h3 {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .feature-content p {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--black);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Tech List */
  .tech-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
    font-family: var(--sans);
  }

  .tech-list li {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--black);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .tech-list li::before {
    content: '‚Üí';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Disclaimer */
  .disclaimer {
    background: var(--accent-light);
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--accent);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .disclaimer .section-title {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  /* Footer */
  .about-footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--black);
  }

  .about-footer p {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--grey);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-container {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    }

    .about-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .intro-text {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-section p {
      font-size: 1.0625rem;
    }

    .feature-item {
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .disclaimer {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
